<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
How can you prepare for a move in Buxton?
</h2>

<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
A little planning makes moving day run far better. Declutter early so you are not paying to move things you no longer want, and label boxes by room so the crew can place them straight away at your new home.
</p>

<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
If you are on a narrow or sloping street, check parking and access in advance and let us know, so we can plan the closest safe spot for the van. For a full step-by-step plan, our <a href="/move-checklist/" class="text-[#071059] hover:underline font-medium">moving house checklist</a> walks you through the weeks before your move.
</p>

<p class="text-gray-700">
Keep an essentials box with documents, chargers, medication and a few basics so you have what you need on the first night without opening every box.
</p>
